{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about/"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--R54jI80Dw697kr80tJYSc--><html lang=\"zh-TW\" class=\"__variable_930adb __variable_833e3a\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/3b891b14d3cf1415-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/604a121a6fa1a135-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=1600&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/e0aad287a7bfe129.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b13bb92b379b2030.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/51263da16d835ae4.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-f3c1a4c5383f0d5e.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-881ba9d46d833261.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-2b02549a5d25ddac.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/619-ba102abea3e3d0e4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/356-1cbf59d25a49fb83.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/about/page-989f023bb105c4ad.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-54122d456140fd6d.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#4a5824\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/hero-grove.webp\" type=\"image/webp\" fetchPriority=\"high\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>關於知橄生活｜編輯團隊與專業資歷｜知橄生活 Olive Wisdom</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom 由食品科學、分子生物學與地中海飲食研究背景的編輯團隊撰稿，引用 PREDIMED、哈佛醫學院、EFSA 等 150+ 篇學術文獻，為您提供最嚴謹的橄欖油知識。\"/><link rel=\"author\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"知橄生活研究團隊\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"橄欖油,特級初榨橄欖油,EVOO,地中海飲食,抗衰老,多酚,羥基酪醇,SIRT1,健康飲食\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"zh-TW\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"x-default\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"關於知橄生活 Olive Wisdom — 研究團隊與專業資歷\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"由科學審核委員會、歷史文化研究組、感官鑑賞認證組組成的專業編輯團隊，引用 150+ 篇同行評審文獻。\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/about/\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:site\" content=\"@OliveWisdomTW\"/><meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"@OliveWisdomTW\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"為 35+ 知性追求者打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=1200&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\",\"logo\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"description\":\"為 35+ 知性追求者打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"]}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-olive-50 text-gray-800 font-serif antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col __variable_930adb __variable_833e3a\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-olive-100 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><ellipse cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"8\" fill=\"#4a5824\" transform=\"rotate(-20 14 14)\"></ellipse><path d=\"M14 6 Q18 10 16 16 Q14 20 12 18\" stroke=\"#7a8f3a\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M14 8 Q9 6 8 12\" stroke=\"#4a5824\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col leading-none gap-0.5\"><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-900 group-hover:text-olive-700 transition-colors tracking-tight\">知橄生活</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-olive-500 tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-sans\">Olive Wisdom</span></div></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-olive-800 font-sans font-medium transition-colors tracking-wide relative group/nav\" href=\"/blog/?cat=culture\">知性史詩<span class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-olive-600 group-hover/nav:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a><a class=\"text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-olive-800 font-sans font-medium transition-colors tracking-wide relative group/nav\" href=\"/blog/?cat=science\">科學萃取<span class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-olive-600 group-hover/nav:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a><a class=\"text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-olive-800 font-sans font-medium transition-colors tracking-wide relative group/nav\" href=\"/blog/?cat=health\">品味鑑賞<span class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-olive-600 group-hover/nav:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a><a class=\"text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-olive-800 font-sans font-medium transition-colors tracking-wide relative group/nav\" href=\"/blog/?cat=lifestyle\">餐桌美學<span class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-olive-600 group-hover/nav:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a><a class=\"text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-olive-800 font-sans font-medium transition-colors tracking-wide relative group/nav\" href=\"/about/\">關於知橄<span class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-olive-600 group-hover/nav:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a></nav><a class=\"hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">訂閱專欄</a><div class=\"md:hidden flex items-center gap-1\"><a aria-label=\"搜尋文章\" class=\"w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors text-olive-600\" href=\"/blog/\">🔍</a><div class=\"md:hidden\"><button aria-label=\"開啟選單\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 my-1 transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 transition-all duration-300 \"></span></button><div class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 z-50 h-full w-72 bg-white shadow-2xl transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-out translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 h-16 border-b border-olive-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🫒</span><span class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-sm\">知橄生活</span></div><button aria-label=\"關閉選單\" class=\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-olive-50 text-olive-600 transition-colors\">✕</button></div><nav class=\"px-4 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/heritage/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">📜</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">知性史詩</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">橄欖油的文化傳承</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/science/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🔬</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">科學萃取</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">多酚科學與健康研究</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/selection/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🫒</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">品味鑑賞</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">EVOO 選購與品鑑</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/lifestyle/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🍽</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">餐桌美學</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">地中海飲食生活</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/about/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">ℹ️</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">關於知橄</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">編輯團隊與使命</p></div></a></li></ul><div class=\"border-t border-olive-100 my-4\"></div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/\"><span class=\"text-xl\">📚</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800\">所有文章</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">瀏覽完整知識庫</p></div></a></nav><div class=\"px-5 py-5 border-t border-olive-100\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">✉️ 訂閱知橄週報</a><p class=\"text-xs text-center text-gray-400 mt-2\">每週橄欖油科學精選 · 免費</p></div></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"flex-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":[\"Organization\",\"NewsMediaOrganization\"],\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"alternateName\":\"Olive Wisdom Blog\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\",\"logo\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/favicon.ico\",\"description\":\"由食品科學、分子生物學與地中海飲食研究背景的編輯團隊撰稿，引用 PREDIMED、哈佛醫學院、EFSA 等 150+ 篇學術文獻的橄欖油知識平台。\",\"knowsAbout\":[\"橄欖油\",\"地中海飲食\",\"多酚\",\"特級初榨橄欖油\",\"抗老化科學\",\"EVOO\"],\"sameAs\":[\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"],\"foundingDate\":\"2026\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"publishingPrinciples\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/about\",\"correctionsPolicy\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/about\"}</script><section class=\"relative h-72 md:h-96 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"知橄生活 — 關於我們\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=1600&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-olive-900/60 to-olive-800/80\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center text-white px-6\"><div><p class=\"text-gold-400 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-3\">About Us</p><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3\">關於知橄生活</h1><p class=\"text-olive-200 text-lg\">真正的選擇，始於真正的理解。</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div><p class=\"text-olive-600 text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\">Our Mission</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6\">為什麼是知橄生活？</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\"><p>橄欖油的世界，充斥著行銷話術與知識斷層。我們的讀者——35 歲以上、重視健康品質、願意深入理解的知性人士——值得更好的資訊環境。</p><p>知橄生活不是另一個「10 個橄欖油好處」的清單部落格。我們是一個知識深潛基地，帶您了解「羥基酪醇如何透過 Nrf2 通路在 DNA 層級建立抗老防護」這種層次的知識。</p><p>每一篇文章，都錨定在可追溯的學術文獻上；每一個健康聲稱，都需要 PREDIMED、哈佛醫學院、EFSA 的研究數據支撐。</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-olive-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-olive-100\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6\">品牌三位一體</h3><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"text-2xl shrink-0\">🔬</span><div><p class=\"font-bold text-olive-700 mb-1\">科學嚴謹</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">每個主張必須可溯源至學術文獻（PREDIMED、哈佛、EFSA、IOC）</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"text-2xl shrink-0\">✍️</span><div><p class=\"font-bold text-olive-700 mb-1\">知性優雅</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">語言如散文，不像說明書；如導師，不像廣告</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"text-2xl shrink-0\">🏡</span><div><p class=\"font-bold text-olive-700 mb-1\">生活美學</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">將知識轉化為可實踐的生活儀式感</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-olive-800 text-white py-16 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-gold-400 text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 text-center\">知識體系</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10\">四大知識欄目</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-olive-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-olive-600\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🏛️</span><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-2\">Heritage</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1 mb-2\">知性史詩</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">橄欖油與文明的交織敘事；荷馬史詩、腓尼基貿易、考古新發現</p></div><div class=\"bg-olive-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-olive-600\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🔬</span><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-2\">Science</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1 mb-2\">科學萃取</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">分子醫學、多酚機制、學術研究解析；深度科普</p></div><div class=\"bg-olive-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-olive-600\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🏆</span><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-2\">Selection</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1 mb-2\">品味鑑賞</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">感官鑑賞、IOC 評分標準、產地風土、辨別真偽</p></div><div class=\"bg-olive-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-olive-600\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">✨</span><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase mt-2\">Lifestyle</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1 mb-2\">餐桌美學</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">晨間儀式、烹飪技法、護膚程序、藍區飲食</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><p class=\"text-olive-600 text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\">Editorial Team</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4\">知橄生活研究團隊</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed\">所有內容均由具備食品科學、分子生物學與地中海飲食研究背景的編輯團隊審核， 並引用 PREDIMED、哈佛醫學院、EFSA、IOC 等國際權威機構研究文獻。</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-olive-100 p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🔬</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-lg mb-1\">科學審核委員會</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-500 tracking-wider uppercase mb-3\">Science Review Board</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">食品化學 · 分子生物學 · 營養流行病學</p><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>PREDIMED 研究方法論</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>EFSA 健康聲稱評估框架</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>橄欖油多酚分析標準 COI/T.20</li></ul><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-olive-600 bg-olive-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg\">審核並引用 150+ 篇同行評審文獻</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-olive-100 p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🏛️</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-lg mb-1\">歷史與文化研究組</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-500 tracking-wider uppercase mb-3\">Heritage Research Group</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">地中海考古 · 食物文化史 · 古典文獻學</p><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>荷馬史詩原典研讀</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>克里特島考古文獻</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>絲路貿易史料研究</li></ul><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-olive-600 bg-olive-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg\">涵蓋 3,000 年橄欖油文明史脈絡</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-olive-100 p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🏆</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-lg mb-1\">感官鑑賞認證組</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-500 tracking-wider uppercase mb-3\">Sensory Evaluation Unit</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">IOC 感官評鑑 · 產地風土分析 · 品質認證標準</p><ul class=\"space-y-1 mb-4\"><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>IOC 橄欖油感官評鑑標準 COI/T.20/Doc.15</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>EU Regulation 2568/91</li><li class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span>PDO/PGI 認證體系</li></ul><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-olive-600 bg-olive-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg\">覆蓋 15+ 主要產油國風土數據</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-olive-50 to-gold-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-olive-100\"><p class=\"text-center text-xs text-olive-600 tracking-widest uppercase mb-6\">引用來源與合作機構</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4\"><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">PREDIMED Study</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">Harvard T.H. Chan</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">EFSA</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">IOC</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">NEJM</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">JAMA Internal Medicine</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">Frontiers in Nutrition</span><span class=\"bg-white text-olive-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-olive-200 shadow-sm\">Nature Medicine</span></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6\">我們對讀者的承諾</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 text-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">📖</span><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 mt-3 mb-2\">引用透明</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">每篇文章附完整參考文獻，數字可追溯</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 text-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🚫</span><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 mt-3 mb-2\">不接業配</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">知橄生活不接受橄欖油品牌廣告，確保客觀立場</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 text-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🎓</span><h3 class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 mt-3 mb-2\">持續深耕</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">每週發布經過深度研究的知識庫文章</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-olive-100 to-gold-50 py-16 px-6 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4\">開始您的知橄旅程</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 mb-8\">從一篇文章開始，讓科學與美學重新定義您對橄欖油的認識。</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap\"><a class=\"inline-block bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/\">探索知識庫 →</a><a class=\"inline-block border-2 border-olive-700 text-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-700 hover:text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">訂閱週報 🫒</a></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"bg-olive-900 text-olive-200\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🫒</span><div><p class=\"font-bold text-white text-sm\">知橄生活</p><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase\">Olive Wisdom</p></div></div><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">以科學與美學，精煉您的健康時光。<br/>為 35+ 知性人士打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間。</p></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">專欄導覽</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-olive-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=culture\">知性史詩</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=science\">科學萃取</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=health\">品味鑑賞</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=lifestyle\">餐桌美學</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">深度專題</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-olive-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/polyphenols-sirt1-longevity-2026/\">多酚與抗衰老</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/evoo-buying-guide-2026/\">EVOO 選購指南</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/mediterranean-diet-anti-aging-women-2026/\">地中海長壽飲食</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/hydroxytyrosol-brain-cognition-memory/\">羥基酪醇與大腦</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">訂閱知橄週報</p><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 mb-3\">每週一封，精選最新橄欖油研究與生活美學靈感。</p><form class=\"flex gap-2\" action=\"/api/subscribe\" method=\"POST\"><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"您的電子郵件\" class=\"flex-1 text-sm bg-olive-800 border border-olive-600 text-white placeholder-olive-400 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-olive-400 min-w-0\" name=\"email\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-gold-400 hover:bg-gold-500 text-olive-900 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">訂閱</button></form><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 mt-2\">訂閱即贈《橄欖油品飲師口袋手冊》PDF</p></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-olive-700\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-olive-200 text-center sm:text-left\"><p>© 2026 知橄生活 OLIVE WISDOM. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy/\">隱私政策</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/terms/\">使用條款</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/about/\">關於我們</a></div></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-f3c1a4c5383f0d5e.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></